sql_query.sql:
SELECT "posts"."id" FROM "posts" WHERE ("posts"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "posts"."topic_id" = 325 AND "posts"."post_type" IN (1, 2, 3) AND "posts"."topic_id" = 325 AND (id = ANY(
          (
            SELECT posts.id
            FROM posts
            WHERE posts.topic_id = 325
            AND posts.post_number = 1
          ) UNION
          (
            SELECT p1.id
            FROM posts p1
            WHERE p1.percent_rank <= 0.2
            AND p1.topic_id = 325
            ORDER BY p1.percent_rank
            LIMIT 100
          )
        )) AND (sort_order > 1) ORDER BY "posts"."sort_order" ASC LIMIT 2

sql_query.sql:
SELECT MAX("posts"."post_number") FROM "posts" WHERE ("posts"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "posts"."topic_id" = 325 AND "posts"."post_type" IN (1, 2, 3) AND "posts"."topic_id" = 325 AND (id = ANY(
          (
            SELECT posts.id
            FROM posts
            WHERE posts.topic_id = 325
            AND posts.post_number = 1
          ) UNION
          (
            SELECT p1.id
            FROM posts p1
            WHERE p1.percent_rank <= 0.2
            AND p1.topic_id = 325
            ORDER BY p1.percent_rank
            LIMIT 100
          )
        ))
